                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2815" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0202</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9291 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">点石成金：中航汽车如何唤醒百年企业耐世特？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Golden Touch: How AVIC Automotive Awaken a Century-old Enterprise Nexteer？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孟添，于晓宇，陈颖颖，孟晓彤，陶向明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学管理学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国航空汽车系统控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">45 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中航汽车；耐世特 ；跨国并购；创新全球化；能力升级；2017百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AVIC Automotive Systems Holdings Co., Ltd, Nexteer, Cross-border Mergers and Acquisitions, Innovation Globalization, Capability Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例回顾了中航汽车并购耐世特的全过程，客观地讲述了中航汽车在制定并购决策、选择并购时机，以及并购整合过程中遇到的困难和解决方案。本案例展示了中航汽车收购耐世特的根本原因，同时揭示了中航汽车通过跨国并购实现技术追赶的内在逻辑。本案例对中国汽车企业如何成功实施跨国并购、以及如何通过“获取先进技术——升级中国市场——实施国际拓展”的三段式创新全球化路径实现能力升级具有重要的实践启示。本案例适用于《创新全球化》、《战略管理》等课程的教学，帮助学生了解跨国并购的全过程，学习和分析跨国并购过程中出现的三个关键问题：跨国并购动因、并购实施与整合、创新全球化路径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case reviews the process of cross-border mergers and acquisitions (M&amp;As), illustrated using the case of AVIC Automotive Systems Holdings Co., Ltd’s acquisition of Nexteer. It objectively describes the main obstacles AVIC Automotive faced at some key points, including the strategic decision on the M&amp;A, the timing of the M&amp;A, and integration after the M&amp;A, as well as the solutions taken by AVIC Automotive’s top management team. Further, the case demonstrates the root cause driving AVIC Automotive to acquire Nexteer, and reveals the internal logic that how AVIC Automotive accomplish technology-pursuing through cross-border M&amp;As. This case has important implications for Chinese automotive enterprises in terms of how to successfully implement a cross-border M&amp;A, and how to implement capability development through three-step innovation globalization, which means acquiring technology, applying technology to the Chinese market and developing overseas market. This case is applicable for curricula such as Innovation Globalization and Strategic Management, offering an opportunity for students (1) to understand the process of cross-border M&amp;As, and (2) to analyze and solve three key problems that Chinese companies face during the process of cross-border M&amp;As: strategic decision-making before M&amp;As, implementation and integration after M&amp;As and the path of innovation globalization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新全球化》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">初创企业的商机识别与开发</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-08</td>
                            </tr>
